	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As a homebrew developer I've often seen awkward and unreasonable game project requests from &quot;idea people&quot;.  However, this time I'd like to help an acquaintance find someone who can do a game I cannot.  I'd like to help him locate and properly proposition a homebrew developer.  Where should he post?  What details are people looking for?<br /><br />Thanks in advance for any help.  A basic search didn't turn up any topic on this (though I could have missed something)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
